Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 1 November 2018. Collage of 9 photos (3x3 grid) with 'Eye am' text on each: Mindfulness, Observer, Darkness, Light, Alertness, Awareness, Love. Heavy black eye makeup in one = Kali/Shiva fierce form. DECODED: 'Eye am' = 'I am' + 'Eye' (third eye). 9 photos in 3x3 = number 9 (Kalki code). Concepts progress through awakening: mindfulness to observation to dark/light to awareness to love. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Avatar Declaration — 'I am everything' — embodiment of all consciousness states.